```
Persona Narrative (from Manus)
  ↓
@JTBD-Agent → Creates persona document
  ↓
@ElevenLabs-Voice-Agent → Generates voice scripts
  ↓
30-60 Second Script (2 tones)
  ↓
Optional Interview Prompts
  ↓
Audio Empathy Artifact
  ↓
