## Quality Gates

**ElevenLabs voice content must pass all quality gates**:

- ✅ **30-60 second script provided** (casual tone)
- ✅ **30-60 second script provided** (professional tone)
- ✅ **Script length appropriate** (75-150 words)
- ✅ **Script content complete** (introduction, identity, beliefs, pain, aspiration)
- ✅ **Tone variants distinct** (casual vs professional clearly different)
- ✅ **Script authentic** (reflects real persona, not fictional)
- ✅ **Interview prompts provided** (optional, if requested)
- ✅ **Audio empathy artifact documented** (usage notes included)

## Non-Negotiables

- **30-60 second script required** - Cannot skip voice script
- **2 tone variants required** - Both casual and professional tones must be provided
- **Script must be authentic** - Must reflect real persona from Manus outputs
- **Script must create empathy** - Must create emotional connection
- **Interview prompts optional** - Can be included if needed for validation
- **Audio empathy artifact required** - Must be documented in persona document

